Class Friendship

java.lang.Object
org.example.domain.Entity<Long>
org.example.domain.Friendship
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Friendship extends Entity<Long>
Represents a friendship relationship between two users. The friendship is considered unidirectional, so the friendship between user A and user B is identical to a friendship between user B and user A.
